{#
  Tabler icon macro — single inline-SVG source for UI icons (issue #18).

  Usage:
    {% import '_icons.html.twig' as ico %}
    {{ ico.icon('movie') }}                  {# default 20px, class "icon" #}
    {{ ico.icon('check', 'text-success') }}  {# extra CSS class #}
    {{ ico.icon('search', '', 16) }}         {# custom size #}

  stroke="currentColor" so icons follow the surrounding text colour and the
  theme picked in /admin/settings. Paths sourced from @tabler/icons (outline;
  a name ending in -filled renders from the filled set: fill, no stroke).
  Size is forced via inline style (not just the width/height attributes) so
  Tabler's contextual `.icon` CSS (1em inside badges/buttons) can't blow it up.
  Unknown names render nothing. Add new icons to the map below as needed.
#}
